thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Thomas Bond

author: Thomas Bond
title: Thomas Bond
text: after ordering two items online, the store rang me personally to tell me one of the items was out of stock and asked which way i would like to proceed, very rare excellent customer service, they then got the item to me in super quick time, no fuss, no hassle... Store DJ will my my first choice from now on.
